## Framework Components

### Data Collection & Preprocessing
- IIT Bombay Hindi-English Parallel Corpus
- Text normalization
- Tokenization
- Sequence truncation and padding

### Transformer-Based Encoding
- MarianMT Encoder
- Contextual embedding generation
- Semantic representation learning

### Attention-Based Decoding
- Self-attention mechanism
- Cross-attention mechanism
- Context-aware translation generation

### Fine-Tuning Module
- Transfer learning using pretrained MarianMT
- Domain adaptation through bilingual sentence pairs
- Contextual optimization via backpropagation

### Translation Generation
- Autoregressive decoding
- Hindi-to-English sequence generation

### Evaluation Module
- BLEU Score
- Translation Error Rate (TER)
- ChrF Score

---

## Dataset

### IIT Bombay Hindi-English Parallel Corpus

- Public bilingual Hindi-English dataset
- Multiple domains including news, literature, and web text
- Fine-tuning performed on train, validation, and test splits

